class:UsersSpec
scenario:Retrieving information about one user

request:
query findOneUser {
  user(id: <id>) {
    id
    username
    firstName
    lastName
    address
    phone
    email
    money
  }
}


response:
{
  "data": {
    "user": [
      {
        "id": <id>,
        "username": <username>,
        "firstName": <firstName>,
        "lastName": <lastName>,
        "address": <address>,
        "phone": <phone>,
        "email": <email>,
        "money": <money>
      }
    ]
  }
}

examples:
=============================================================================================================================================================
| *should                       | id | username          | firstName  | lastName   | address        | phone         | email                        | money  |
=============================================================================================================================================================
| "retrieve user with given id" | 1  | "miloradvojnovic" | "Milorad"  | "Vojnovic" | "Puskinova 27" | "06978954558" | "milorad.vojnovic@gmail.com" | 100000 |
=============================================================================================================================================================


response:
{
  "data": {
    "user": null
  }
}

